title: VA - The Best Latino Carnival In The World ...Ever! (1997)@flac
description: This compilation has most of the top latin hits around and is EXCELLENT for parties. The first CD is amazing with tracks like Bamboleo, Lambada,Samba De Janeiro and Tequila just to name a few. The second CD is also quite good with tracks such as Guantenamera and Light My Fire. If you like Latin Music, you will love this CD and this is the best Latin compilation I have ever come across. Usually they just have a few good songs and are loaded with crap songs whose titles look good(as they are in Spanish). But this one is different which is exactly why you should buy it!
